author: AddictedToStyrene
title: Just a little truck
review: What you see is what you get. This set came as one of three randomised sets in some Danish biscuits. It's nothing special, and it is a bit smaller and less interesting than the Hot Wheels/Matchbox scaled Tiny Turbos. But, it came in a tin of yummy biscuits, and it is cute to roll around a desk.
